
Reduce unnecessary debug logic checks:
- Rename OD_DEBUG_CHECK to OD_DEBUG_EVAL - this is only evaluated in debug
- Add OD_DEBUG_CHECK - always  evaluated, but the result is only checked in debug (else result discarded into a no-op inline function)
- OD_CHECK - always, evaluated and the result always used

Entity rendering optimizations:
- Vertex cache by depth, odArrayT<odFastArray<odVertex>>



